OpenFX — the OFX image effect plug-in API
https://github.com/AcademySoftwareFoundation/openfx
Licence: BSD 3-Clause
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Fetched at build time (tag OFX_Release_1.5.1). The OpenFX C++ Support library is
compiled into the plugin. Not redistributed in source form here.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ONNX Runtime
https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime
Licence: MIT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Fetched at build time and bundled inside the .ofx.bundle as a privately-renamed
shared library (libonnxruntime_hyp.* / onnxruntime_hyp.dll). Release artifacts
DO redistribute this binary.

On Windows the bundled build is a static-CRT build of ONNX Runtime produced for
the humbaba project and hosted at
https://github.com/samhodge-tokgan/humbaba/releases — still MIT-licensed ONNX
Runtime, rebuilt with --enable_msvc_static_runtime.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
humbaba — Depth Anything 3 OpenFX plugin
https://github.com/samhodge-tokgan/humbaba
Licence: Apache-2.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The cross-platform OFX + ONNX Runtime scaffolding in this repository is adapted
from humbaba: the CMake build and bundle assembly, the private-runtime renaming,
packaging/ofx_exports.*, src/OrtAccel.h, src/WinLoader.cpp, and the headless
Natron test harness.
